Question: Each image includes one hog standing on all fours in a field, and no image includes a human.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://www.sundaypost.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2017/06/iStock-186545340-900x540.jpg

Right image URL: http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2015/01/07/006D73F400000258-0-image-m-10_1420671408863.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many hogs are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many hogs are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the hog standing on all fours in a field?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the hog standing on all fours in a field?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a human in the image?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a human in the image?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2} and not {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3} and not {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} and {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
